text: Since inception in 2005, there have been 13 clubs who have played in the A-League. Nine clubs have won the A-League Premiership, they are Sydney FC (4 times), Melbourne Victory (3 times), Adelaide United (2 times), Brisbane Roar (2 times), Central Coast Mariners (2 times), Perth
